long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is the Makul Sözlük  - Turkmen to English digital and audio dictionary. This dictionary includes more than 15,000 key words. You can find English translations of more than 25,000 Turkmen words. The main feature of the Makul Sözlük project is that it is the first "speaking" dictionary in Turkmen. You can listen to these words out loud, not just the Turkmen and English written versions of the words.
